text: The 1989/90 NTFL season was the 69th season of the Northern Territory Football League (NTFL). St Marys have won there 16th premiership title while defeating the Darwin Buffaloes in the grand final by 108 points. ==Grand Final== {| class="wikitable" style="text-align:left;" |- style="background:#efefef;" !
